35ce609c0f34d88b3cd3a2edc6b7bc4332de9b06ad9b57a2fcc54c655399ad8e426b224e064d86146ccc1258ae7cb58a33d6187e7d5f396888a1d5a61637c940  0001-support-for-Lua-5.2.patch"
